Phantasmal Armour is a waste of time, it offers no improvement over 52 Phantom Armour and costs more to cast.  I believe it drops off a boss mob in SSRA Temple.  Don't bother.<br>
Veil of the Elements drops off underbulks in Fungus Grove, but is common in the bazaar.  Must get.<br>
Bandoleer of Luclin is rare (Western Wastes, I think, but don't quote me).  I think someone once asked me summon daggers but that may have just been out of curiosity...  Get it for completeness but don't pay more than you have to.<br>
Scars of Sigil I've personally seen drop lots of time, can't remember where, but it's very cheap in the bazaar.  Must get. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=274972" target="top">Chard</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->, 59 Conjurer</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=skildpade>skildpade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 226<br> <font color=#333333>(3/3/03 3:34:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1874.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 54 spells advice please</span><hr size=1> After the summoned focus stuff and Trods are, in my experience, the most popular sommoned objects, quiver of marr, bandoler of luclin and pouch of quellious.<br>
