<br>
It also is very useful to take down a low-on-health mob as it starts to sprint out of the room to collect its buddies.<br>
<br>
Scars or Scintillation (depending on situation) are one of my &quot;always memmed&quot; spells for just that reason. Not quite as much of a lifesaver as Gate, but damn close...<br>
